# pyenv
#   For a library or package, you might want to ignore these files since the code is
#   intended to run in multiple environments; otherwise, check them in:
# .python-version

# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#1255, pipenv should generally check in Pipfile.lock.
#   For libraries, see also https://pipenv.pydantic.dev/en/stable/advanced/#pipfile-vs-setup.py
# Pipfile.lock

# poetry
#   Similar to Pipfile.lock, poetry.lock should generally be checked in.
# poetry.lock

# pdm
#   Similar to Pipfile.lock, pdm.lock should generally be checked in.
# pdm.lock

